snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Firesong Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Conclude your Legacy of the Bretons saga in The Elder Scrolls Online: Firesong, now available on PC/Mac and coming November 15 for Xbox and PlayStation consoles.

Discover an all-new zone, the mysterious island of Galen, and storyline that dives deep into the lives and lore of the druids of the Systres who call Galen home. Battle the Ascendant Order and bring your year-long adventure to its epic conclusion with bonus content for those who also completed the High Isle Chapter storyline.

The Firesong DLC is now available via ESO Plus membership or in the in-game Crown Store for PC/Mac and arrives on Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5 on November 15.

Official Site: https://www.elderscrollsonline.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/ElderScrollsOnline
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TESOnline
Instagram: https://instagram.com/elderscrollsonline

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood and Gore, Sexual Themes, Use of Alcohol, and Violence. Online interactions not rated by the ESRB.
